releases.body:
Improve installation process for Mac and Windows by
- switching to packaging distribution releases with [electron-builder](https://github.com/electron-userland/electron-builder)
- distributing an executable installer for Windows and a DMG installer for Mac

v1.0 is here! ðŸŽ‰ 

Lot's of great new features:
- A new RESTFUL API
- Support for scheduling and saving queries
- Support for S3, Elasticsearch, Apache Drill in addition to Postgres, Redshift, MySQL, MSSQL, Mariadb, SQLite
- Support for loading and saving credentials on disk
- A command-line version of the app
- A web-app version of the app
- Over 100 tests
